  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[LINUX常用网络命令]]></title>
    <link href="http://haowaiwai.github.io/blog/2014/02/24/linuxchang-yong-wang-luo-ming-ling/"/>
    <updated>2014-02-24T18:09:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://haowaiwai.github.io/blog/2014/02/24/linuxchang-yong-wang-luo-ming-ling</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>查看当前监听80端口的程序</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>lsof -i :80</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>查看当前网卡的物理地址</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>ifconfig eth0 | head -1 | awk '{print $5}'</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>同一个网卡增加第二个IP地址</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>#在网卡eth0上增加一个1.2.3.4的IP：
</span><span class='line'>sudo ifconfig eth0:0 1.2.3.4 netmask 255.255.255.0
</span><span class='line'>#删除增加的IP：
</span><span class='line'>sudo ifconfig eth0:0 down</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>立即让网络支持nat</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>echo 1 | sudo tee /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward
</span><span class='line'>sudo iptables -t nat -I POSTROUTING -j MASQUERADE</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>查看路由信息</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>netstat -rn
</span><span class='line'>sudo route -n</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>增加和删除路由</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>sudo route add -net 192.168.0.0 netmask 255.255.255.0 gw 172.16.0.1
</span><span class='line'>sudo route del -net 192.168.0.0 netmask 255.255.255.0 gw 172.16.0.1</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>统计当前IP连接的个数</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>netstat -na|grep ESTABLISHED|awk '{print $5}'|awk -F: '{print $1}'|sort|uniq -c|sort -r -n
</span><span class='line'>netstat -na|grep SYN|awk '{print $5}'|awk -F: '{print $1}'|sort|uniq -c|sort -r -n
</span><span class='line'>netstat -ntu | awk '{print $5}' | cut -d: -f1 | sort | uniq -c | sort -n</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
